    "By Fact 4.44, h satisfies ⊑-forth, so ζ F (x) ⊑ (F b)p X implies h(ζ F (x)) ⊑ G h(X), contradicting what we obtained above.",
    "Thus, g[X] ⊑ G h(X).",
